      "usage": {
        "subtype": "usage",
        "text": "worn horseshoes",
        "type": "stat_block_section"
      }
    },
    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "When you affix these simple iron horseshoes to the hooves of an ordinary horse or a quadrupedal animal companion and the animal companion invests them, that creature gains a +5-foot item bonus to its land Speed and a +2 item bonus to Athletics checks to High Jump and Long Jump. In addition, when it Leaps, it can move 5 feet farther if jumping horizontally or 3 feet higher if jumping vertically.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 29,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "354c1f98bc548150ddf224becffcd680",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "animal companion",
            "href": "AnimalCompanions.aspx",
            "name": "animal companion",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Companion",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 218,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "GM Core pg. 272",
              "aonid": 218,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "GM Core pg. 272",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "GM Core",
            "page": 272,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "An item with this trait can be worn by an animal companion or similar creature. A companion can have up to two items invested.",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 98,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "56b56ea5f9d865dc549f0ed7372ab504",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "invest",
            "aonid": 2799,
            "game-obj": "Actions",
            "name": "invest",
            "type": "link"
          }
        ],
        "name": "Invested",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 218,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "GM Core pg. 219",
              "aonid": 218,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "GM Core pg. 219",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "GM Core",
            "page": 219,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "A character can invest only 10 magical items that have the invested trait. None of the magical effects of the item apply if the character hasn\u2019t invested it, nor can it be activated, though the character still gains any normal benefits from wearing the physical item (like a hat keeping rain off their head).",
        "type": "trait"
      },
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 134,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "trait"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "60a4f011afd1e0fac8211bd01108d104",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "name": "Primal",
        "sources": [
          {
            "errata": {
              "alt": "2.0",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "2.0",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "link": {
              "alt": "Player Core pg. 460",
              "aonid": 216,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Player Core pg. 460",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Player Core",
            "page": 460,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "This magic comes from the primal tradition, connecting to the natural world and instinct. Anything with this trait is magical.  \n  \nA creature with this trait is primarily constituted of or has a strong connection to primal magic.",
        "type": "trait"
      }
    ],
